# Trivy vulnerability ignore list
#
# Format: one CVE / advisory ID per line. Trivy auto-loads this file when
# present at the scan working directory. The aquasecurity/trivy-action
# honours it for both filesystem and image scans.
#
# Each entry must include a justification comment so future reviewers can
# decide whether the ignore is still warranted.

